				I think healthcare is a *right* in an advanced civilisation.
<br />

<br />
Do I like capitalism?  No.  Do I believe in Capitalism?  Yes.  Do I like Communism?  Yes.  Do I believe in Communism?  No.  Could 1 day we be ready for Communism?  Doubtfull...maybe with a HUGE AI running the government...maybe...if they can motivate the individuals as well...we need our day to day candy, if you want me to do that extra work, I need a candy...and not any candy, a candy I want BAD!
<br />

<br />
We really should privatised until we understand more and figure more around.  Now we are failing like clowns and the Canadians doctors move the the US, and the richs Canadians that are sick go get some healthcare in the US, which are 2 very undesirable effects.  As long as the borders are open and the folks move freely, we cant have a public healthcare efficient unless everyone does it...and nobody around plan to do it, so no point in holding to a dream that cannot come true.<br />
